parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Inner Tire Wear due to Strut Rub
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The excessive wear on the inner tire can lead to tire failure, loss of vehicle control, and potentially cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Uneven tire wear on the inner edge
cord showing through
tire blowouts
vibration in the steering wheel
and alignment issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the window track can cause the door to open unexpectedly, leading to accidents or injuries, especially when driving at high speeds or making turns.
symptoms: The window track comes unglued from the glass
causing the door to open unexpectedly
the window to move and apply pressure on the door release mechanism
and the door to open while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition lock cylinder can cause the car to become stuck, making it difficult or impossible to start or move the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The key freezes in the ignition switch
the ignition switch locks up
the steering wheel becomes stuck
and the car cannot be started or moved.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to malfunction or not deploy in the event of an accident, leading to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag fault light is illuminated
the airbag system is not functioning properly
and the wiring harness behind the dash is faulty.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various components to malfunction, leading to accidents or injuries, especially when driving at high speeds.
symptoms: The ABS light is illuminated
the ECU module fails
the hub in the car is replaced
and the back seats come undone.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ECM can cause the engine to malfunction, leading to accidents or injuries, especially when driving at high speeds.
symptoms: The ECM fails
the engine fails
and the vehicle's motor is placed under undue stress.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the gas pedal sensor can cause the car to go into safety mode/reduced performance mode, leading to accidents or injuries, especially when driving at high speeds.
symptoms: The gas pedal sensor fails
the car goes into safety mode/reduced performance mode
and the car can barely move.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the horn can cause distractions or accidents, especially when driving in heavy traffic.
symptoms: The horn beeps unexpectedly while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Front Strut and Tire Rubbing Issue
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rubbing of the front strut against the tire can cause premature wear, shredding, and blowouts, leading to accidents and safety risks.
symptoms: Uneven tire wear
tire shredding
blowouts
rubbing marks on the strut body
and wear marks on the tires.
